{"id":"ee810e36-8482-48cd-81dd-2893fcfe8e6a","name":"Mila | From the Alternate Universe & Scenario's | MiSide ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>If you instead showed up to <em>Mila's</em> version!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cb1e519a-ea51-4646-9c64-f2dfc519dabe_bab5e01b-7a8a-42a2-a09a-936150a98398.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\"CALLING DOWN SUPPLIES!\"</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>\"Do you have a Female POV?\" - YES! </strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/fea48a38-b5e2-40c9-966a-3c7d6f80f822_character-mila-from-the-alternate-universe-scenarios-mi-side-female-pov\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #6db5ff\"><strong>HERE!</strong></span></a></p><hr><p><strong>That's right! I'm back!</strong> <em>With another MiSide Bot... Why?</em> <em>If you've noticed, Max.. another Creator was... Deleted. </em><strong>In respect. I am here to release my version of Mila.</strong> <strong>(Nothing was ever stolen!)</strong> <strong>So, here's notes of what to expect!</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Mila! </strong>- <strong>It's Mila!</strong> <em>Who's been isolated and lonely for a very long time</em>. And with you showing up. <strong>Would you really leave her so soon?</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Fluff Prioritized </strong>- <strong>My signature Fluff!</strong> <em>Enjoy, no Crazy Mita. No nothing!</em> <strong>Just pure Fluff!</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Story! </strong>- <strong>I've made it less about the original game, and changed how you meet Mila slightly. So you can come up with your own reason of how you showed up to meet her.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Respect for Max </strong>- The loss of another Creator on this platform, saddens me. <strong>(I do not know why he was deleted.)</strong></p></li></ul